FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."AccessFailedCount", t."ConcurrencyStamp", t."Email", t."EmailConfirmed", t."LockoutEnabled", t."LockoutEnd", t."NormalizedEmail", t."NormalizedUserName", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t."SecurityStamp", t."TwoFactorEnabled", t."UserName", t."Id0", t."AccessToken", t."AvatarUrl", t."HtmlUrl", t."Login", t."UserId", p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id", t0."Name", t0."OwnerId"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

SELECT t."Id", t."AccessFailedCount", t."ConcurrencyStamp", t."Email", t."EmailConfirmed", t."LockoutEnabled", t."LockoutEnd", t."NormalizedEmail", t."NormalizedUserName", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t."SecurityStamp", t."TwoFactorEnabled", t."UserName", t."Id0", t."AccessToken", t."AvatarUrl", t."HtmlUrl", t."Login", t."UserId", p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id", t0."Name", t0."OwnerId"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."OwnerId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p1 ON p0."ProjectId" = p1."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."ContributorId", t0."ProjectId", t0."Id"

    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"

    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"

) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"

    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))

) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"

    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"

    FROM "Invites" AS i

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", a."Id" AS "Id0", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId", r."UserId"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON p."OwnerId" = a."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p."Id" = r."ProjectId"
    WHERE (p."Id" = @__id_0) AND (@__id_0 IS NOT NULL)
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AccessFailedCount", a0."ConcurrencyStamp", a0."Email", a0."EmailConfirmed", a0."LockoutEnabled", a0."LockoutEnd", a0."NormalizedEmail", a0."NormalizedUserName", a0."PasswordHash", a0."PhoneNumber", a0."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a0."SecurityStamp", a0."TwoFactorEnabled", a0."UserName"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a0 ON i."UserId" = a0."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", a1."Id", a1."AccessFailedCount", a1."ConcurrencyStamp", a1."Email", a1."EmailConfirmed", a1."LockoutEnabled", a1."LockoutEnd", a1."NormalizedEmail", a1."NormalizedUserName", a1."PasswordHash", a1."PhoneNumber", a1."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a1."SecurityStamp", a1."TwoFactorEnabled", a1."UserName"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0

) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t2."Id", t2."Description", t2."Name", t2."ProjectId", t2."Status", t3."AssigneeId", t3."TicketId", t3."AssignedUserId", t3."Id" AS "Id0", t3."AccessFailedCount", t3."ConcurrencyStamp", t3."Email", t3."EmailConfirmed", t3."LockoutEnabled", t3."LockoutEnd", t3."NormalizedEmail", t3."NormalizedUserName", t3."PasswordHash", t3."PhoneNumber", t3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t3."SecurityStamp", t3."TwoFactorEnabled", t3."UserName"

        SELECT a2."AssigneeId", a2."TicketId", a2."AssignedUserId", a3."Id", a3."AccessFailedCount", a3."ConcurrencyStamp", a3."Email", a3."EmailConfirmed", a3."LockoutEnabled", a3."LockoutEnd", a3."NormalizedEmail", a3."NormalizedUserName", a3."PasswordHash", a3."PhoneNumber", a3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a3."SecurityStamp", a3."TwoFactorEnabled", a3."UserName"
        FROM "Assignees" AS a2
        LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a3 ON a2."AssignedUserId" = a3."Id"
    ) AS t3 ON t2."Id" = t3."TicketId"
) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id", t4."Id", t4."AssigneeId", t4."TicketId"

    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p."Id" = r."ProjectId"

) AS t

) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ProjectId"

    SELECT t2."Id", t2."Description", t2."Name", t2."ProjectId", t2."Status", t3."AssigneeId", t3."TicketId", t3."AssignedUserId", t3."Id" AS "Id0", t3."AccessFailedCount", t3."ConcurrencyStamp", t3."Email", t3."EmailConfirmed", t3."LockoutEnabled", t3."LockoutEnd", t3."NormalizedEmail", t3."NormalizedUserName", t3."PasswordHash", t3."PhoneNumber", t3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t3."SecurityStamp", t3."TwoFactorEnabled", t3."UserName"
    FROM "Tickets" AS t2
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT a2."AssigneeId", a2."TicketId", a2."AssignedUserId", a3."Id", a3."AccessFailedCount", a3."ConcurrencyStamp", a3."Email", a3."EmailConfirmed", a3."LockoutEnabled", a3."LockoutEnd", a3."NormalizedEmail", a3."NormalizedUserName", a3."PasswordHash", a3."PhoneNumber", a3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a3."SecurityStamp", a3."TwoFactorEnabled", a3."UserName"
        FROM "Assignees" AS a2
        LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a3 ON a2."AssignedUserId" = a3."Id"
    ) AS t3 ON t2."Id" = t3."TicketId"
) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id", t4."Id", t4."AssigneeId", t4."TicketId"

        LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a3 ON a2."AssignedUserId" = a3."Id"
    ) AS t3 ON t2."Id" = t3."TicketId"
) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id", t4."Id", t4."AssigneeId", t4."TicketId"

) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"

    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p."Id" = r."ProjectId"
    WHERE (p."Id" = @__id_0) AND (@__id_0 IS NOT NULL)
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AccessFailedCount", a0."ConcurrencyStamp", a0."Email", a0."EmailConfirmed", a0."LockoutEnabled", a0."LockoutEnd", a0."NormalizedEmail", a0."NormalizedUserName", a0."PasswordHash", a0."PhoneNumber", a0."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a0."SecurityStamp", a0."TwoFactorEnabled", a0."UserName"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a0 ON i."UserId" = a0."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", a1."Id", a1."AccessFailedCount", a1."ConcurrencyStamp", a1."Email", a1."EmailConfirmed", a1."LockoutEnabled", a1."LockoutEnd", a1."NormalizedEmail", a1."NormalizedUserName", a1."PasswordHash", a1."PhoneNumber", a1."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a1."SecurityStamp", a1."TwoFactorEnabled", a1."UserName"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0

) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t2."Id", t2."Description", t2."Name", t2."ProjectId", t2."Status", t3."AssigneeId", t3."TicketId", t3."Id" AS "Id0", t3."AccessFailedCount", t3."ConcurrencyStamp", t3."Email", t3."EmailConfirmed", t3."LockoutEnabled", t3."LockoutEnd", t3."NormalizedEmail", t3."NormalizedUserName", t3."PasswordHash", t3."PhoneNumber", t3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t3."SecurityStamp", t3."TwoFactorEnabled", t3."UserName"
    FROM "Tickets" AS t2
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT a2."AssigneeId", a2."TicketId", a3."Id", a3."AccessFailedCount", a3."ConcurrencyStamp", a3."Email", a3."EmailConfirmed", a3."LockoutEnabled", a3."LockoutEnd", a3."NormalizedEmail", a3."NormalizedUserName", a3."PasswordHash", a3."PhoneNumber", a3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a3."SecurityStamp", a3."TwoFactorEnabled", a3."UserName"
        FROM "Assignees" AS a2
        INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a3 ON a2."AssigneeId" = a3."Id"
    ) AS t3 ON t2."Id" = t3."TicketId"
) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id", t4."Id", t4."AssigneeId", t4."TicketId", t4."Id0"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", a."Id" AS "Id0", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId", r."UserId"
    FROM "Projects" AS p
    LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON p."OwnerId" = a."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p."Id" = r."ProjectId"
    WHERE (p."Id" = @__id_0) AND (@__id_0 IS NOT NULL)
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AccessFailedCount", a0."ConcurrencyStamp", a0."Email", a0."EmailConfirmed", a0."LockoutEnabled", a0."LockoutEnd", a0."NormalizedEmail", a0."NormalizedUserName", a0."PasswordHash", a0."PhoneNumber", a0."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a0."SecurityStamp", a0."TwoFactorEnabled", a0."UserName"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a0 ON i."UserId" = a0."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", a1."Id", a1."AccessFailedCount", a1."ConcurrencyStamp", a1."Email", a1."EmailConfirmed", a1."LockoutEnabled", a1."LockoutEnd", a1."NormalizedEmail", a1."NormalizedUserName", a1."PasswordHash", a1."PhoneNumber", a1."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a1."SecurityStamp", a1."TwoFactorEnabled", a1."UserName"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p0
    INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a1 ON p0."ContributorId" = a1."Id"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t2."Id", t2."Description", t2."Name", t2."ProjectId", t2."Status", t3."AssigneeId", t3."TicketId", t3."Id" AS "Id0", t3."AccessFailedCount", t3."ConcurrencyStamp", t3."Email", t3."EmailConfirmed", t3."LockoutEnabled", t3."LockoutEnd", t3."NormalizedEmail", t3."NormalizedUserName", t3."PasswordHash", t3."PhoneNumber", t3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t3."SecurityStamp", t3."TwoFactorEnabled", t3."UserName"

        SELECT a2."AssigneeId", a2."TicketId", a3."Id", a3."AccessFailedCount", a3."ConcurrencyStamp", a3."Email", a3."EmailConfirmed", a3."LockoutEnabled", a3."LockoutEnd", a3."NormalizedEmail", a3."NormalizedUserName", a3."PasswordHash", a3."PhoneNumber", a3."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a3."SecurityStamp", a3."TwoFactorEnabled", a3."UserName"
        FROM "Assignees" AS a2

    ) AS t3 ON t2."Id" = t3."TicketId"
) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"

SELECT t."Id", t."AccessFailedCount", t."ConcurrencyStamp", t."Email", t."EmailConfirmed", t."LockoutEnabled", t."LockoutEnd", t."NormalizedEmail", t."NormalizedUserName", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t."SecurityStamp", t."TwoFactorEnabled", t."UserName", t."Id0", t."AccessToken", t."AvatarUrl", t."HtmlUrl", t."Login", t."UserId", p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", t0."Id", t0."Message", t0."ProjectId", t0."Status", t0."UserId", t0."Id0", t0."Name", t0."OwnerId", t0."Id1", t0."Description", t0."HtmlUrl", t0."Name0", t0."ProjectId0", t0."UserId0", r0."Id", r0."Description", r0."HtmlUrl", r0."Name", r0."ProjectId", r0."UserId", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id", t1."Name", t1."OwnerId", t1."Id0", t1."Description", t1."HtmlUrl", t1."Name0", t1."ProjectId0", t1."UserId"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

    LIMIT 2
) AS t

    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AccessFailedCount", a0."ConcurrencyStamp", a0."Email", a0."EmailConfirmed", a0."LockoutEnabled", a0."LockoutEnd", a0."NormalizedEmail", a0."NormalizedUserName", a0."PasswordHash", a0."PhoneNumber", a0."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a0."SecurityStamp", a0."TwoFactorEnabled", a0."UserName"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", a."Id" AS "Id0", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId", r."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON p."OwnerId" = a."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p."Id" = r."ProjectId"
    WHERE (p."Id" = @__id_0) AND (@__id_0 IS NOT NULL)

) AS t

    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AccessFailedCount", a0."ConcurrencyStamp", a0."Email", a0."EmailConfirmed", a0."LockoutEnabled", a0."LockoutEnd", a0."NormalizedEmail", a0."NormalizedUserName", a0."PasswordHash", a0."PhoneNumber", a0."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a0."SecurityStamp", a0."TwoFactorEnabled", a0."UserName"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", a1."Id", a1."AccessFailedCount", a1."ConcurrencyStamp", a1."Email", a1."EmailConfirmed", a1."LockoutEnabled", a1."LockoutEnd", a1."NormalizedEmail", a1."NormalizedUserName", a1."PasswordHash", a1."PhoneNumber", a1."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a1."SecurityStamp", a1."TwoFactorEnabled", a1."UserName"

LEFT JOIN (

) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"

) AS t

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."ProjectId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ContributorId", p0."ProjectId", a1."Id", a1."AccessFailedCount", a1."ConcurrencyStamp", a1."Email", a1."EmailConfirmed", a1."LockoutEnabled", a1."LockoutEnd", a1."NormalizedEmail", a1."NormalizedUserName", a1."PasswordHash", a1."PhoneNumber", a1."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a1."SecurityStamp", a1."TwoFactorEnabled", a1."UserName"

        FROM "Assignees" AS a2

    ) AS t3 ON t2."Id" = t3."TicketId"
) AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."ProjectId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id", t4."Id", t4."AssigneeId", t4."TicketId", t4."Id0"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

2019-12-19 16:36:42.283 +03:00 [INF] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0='?'], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."AccessFailedCount", t."ConcurrencyStamp", t."Email", t."EmailConfirmed", t."LockoutEnabled", t."LockoutEnd", t."NormalizedEmail", t."NormalizedUserName", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t."SecurityStamp", t."TwoFactorEnabled", t."UserName", t."Id0", t."AccessToken", t."AvatarUrl", t."HtmlUrl", t."Login", t."UserId", p."Id", p."Name", p."OwnerId", t0."Id", t0."Message", t0."ProjectId", t0."Status", t0."UserId", t0."Id0", t0."Name", t0."OwnerId", t0."Id1", t0."Description", t0."HtmlUrl", t0."Name0", t0."ProjectId0", t0."UserId0", r0."Id", r0."Description", r0."HtmlUrl", r0."Name", r0."ProjectId", r0."UserId", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id", t1."Name", t1."OwnerId", t1."Id0", t1."Description", t1."HtmlUrl", t1."Name0", t1."ProjectId0", t1."UserId"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName", g."Id" AS "Id0", g."AccessToken", g."AvatarUrl", g."HtmlUrl", g."Login", g."UserId"
    FROM "AspNetUsers" AS a
    LEFT JOIN "GithubUsers" AS g ON a."Id" = g."UserId"
    WHERE ((a."UserName" = @__authState_User_Identity_Name_0) AND ((a."UserName" IS NOT NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NOT NULL))) OR ((a."UserName" IS NULL) AND (@__authState_User_Identity_Name_0 IS NULL))
    LIMIT 2
) AS t
LEFT JOIN "Projects" AS p ON t."Id" = p."OwnerId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT i."Id", i."Message", i."ProjectId", i."Status", i."UserId", p0."Id" AS "Id0", p0."Name", p0."OwnerId", r."Id" AS "Id1", r."Description", r."HtmlUrl", r."Name" AS "Name0", r."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r."UserId" AS "UserId0"
    FROM "Invites" AS i
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p0 ON i."ProjectId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r ON p0."Id" = r."ProjectId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r0 ON t."Id" = r0."UserId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."ContributorId", p1."ProjectId", p2."Id", p2."Name", p2."OwnerId", r1."Id" AS "Id0", r1."Description", r1."HtmlUrl", r1."Name" AS "Name0", r1."ProjectId" AS "ProjectId0", r1."UserId"
    FROM "ProjectUsers" AS p1
    INNER JOIN "Projects" AS p2 ON p1."ProjectId" = p2."Id"
    LEFT JOIN "Repositories" AS r1 ON p2."Id" = r1."ProjectId"
) AS t1 ON t."Id" = t1."ContributorId"
ORDER BY t."Id", p."Id", t0."Id", t0."Id0", r0."Id", t1."ContributorId", t1."ProjectId", t1."Id"
